Packed with Kaolin clay. It's the perfect cleanser for your skin.

description: Product Description Our cleansing mud mask smells of fresh Cucumbers, so if you enjoy the fun of applying a mask, you will love this skin treat. We use Kaolin as it's the perfect cleanser, helping to remove impurities + dirt from the skin. Ingredients Aqua, Kaolin, Cetearyl Alcohol, Talc, Steareth-20, Stearic Acid, Glyceryl Stearate, DMDM Hydantoin, Methylparaben, Parfum, Propylparaben, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Benzyl Salicylate, Linalool, CI 19140, CI 42090. Directions On freshly cleansed skin, apply a thin layer with fingertips or a mask brush (avoiding eye, lips & eyebrows) allow 10 minutes for the mask to take effect. Wash off using a hot cloth and dry. Use as a weekly treatment alongside our Face Facts serums & moisturisers to complete your skincare routine. See more
